OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe heatwave across the UK looks set
OL,8,Fto continue into next week as 2026
OL,9,Fbecame the first year to record
OL,10,Ftemperatures above 35C on six separate
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,13,FEmergency services have warned of
OL,14,F"extreme" wildfire risks over the
OL,15,Fweekend, with the London Fire Brigade
OL,16,F(LFB) urging people not to use
OL,17,Fdisposable barbecues for fear of the
OL,18,Fdry heat sparking fires.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
