PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783871341
OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe force reported that it was dealing
OL,8,Fwith a moorland fire near Arnfield
OL,9,FFarm in Glossop and a separate ongoing
OL,10,Ffire in Tintwistle Moor.
OL,12,FFriday night also saw a "trackside"
OL,13,Fblaze involving shrubbery at Stratford
OL,14,FStation in London at around 7pm,
OL,15,Fcausing rail line closures.
OL,17,FLFB reported that the fire was under
OL,18,Fcontrol at around 9.30pm, and has used
OL,19,Fthe incident to reiterate the risk of
OL,20,Fwildfires during the heatwave this
OL,21,Fweekend.
OL,26,@tD@YOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
