PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783871341
OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe brigade said that the latest
OL,8,Fassessments show the risk in London
OL,9,Fwill grow from "elevated" to "extreme"
OL,10,Ffrom Saturday to Monday, driven by
OL,11,Ffactors like prolonged dry weather,
OL,12,Fheat and wind speed.
OL,14,FLFB assistant commissioner Tom Goodall
OL,15,Fsaid: "We want everyone across the
OL,16,Fcity to enjoy the continuing heatwave
OL,17,Fbut this must be done responsibly."
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@YO]qD@^OUqD@fO]wD@GOU
