OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FDerbyshire Constabulary announced that
OL,8,Fthe body of an 18-year-old man had
OL,9,Fbeen recovered from the water near the
OL,10,Fweir at the Darley Abbey Mills complex
OL,11,Fafter two teenagers got into
OL,12,Fdifficulty.
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police said a scene
OL,15,Fremained in place at Dovestone
OL,16,FReservoir, Oldham, after an 18-year-
OL,17,Fold man died on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
