OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe Met Office warned people planning
OL,8,Fto enjoy the water this weekend to be
OL,9,Fcareful and check the water
OL,10,Ftemperature to avoid cold water shocks.
OL,12,FThe former 35C on separate days record
OL,13,Fwas held by 1976 and 2020 during which
OL,14,Ffive days were recorded with
OL,15,Ftemperatures over 35C.
OL,17,F2026 has also become the first year to
OL,18,Fsee temperatures of 35C or higher in
OL,19,Fthree calendar months ` and broke the
OL,20,Frecord for most temperatures of 34C or
OL,21,Fhigher, with nine so far this summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
