OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWater firms have also announced
OL,13,Fhosepipe bans for the east of England,
OL,14,FCambridge, Hampshire, the Isle of
OL,15,FWight and areas of Kent.
OL,17,FOn Friday morning, Anglian Water also
OL,18,Fannounced a hosepipe ban for its more
OL,19,Fthan five million customers in the
OL,20,Feast of England
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
