OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,F.The ban will come into force from 1am
OL,8,Fon Saturday but the utility has asked
OL,9,Fthat people "live within the spirit of
OL,10,Fthese restrictions immediately".
OL,12,FIn a notice on Thursday afternoon,
OL,13,FCambridge Water announced a temporary
OL,14,Fhosepipe ban for its 350,000
OL,15,Fcustomers, which came into effect
OL,16,Fimmediately but enforcement actions
OL,17,Fwill not start until 1am on July 17.
OL,26,@qD@MOUrD@_O]
