OL,3,CHeatwave to last until next week as
OL,4,Cemergency services warn of wildfire
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThis marks the first time in three
OL,8,Fdecades it has introduced the
OL,9,Frestriction, with the company saying
OL,10,Fteams are working around the clock to
OL,11,Fmaintain supplies.
OL,13,FSouth East Water became the first to
OL,14,Fintroduce a ban on July 3 for areas of
OL,15,FKent, including those in Ashford,
OL,16,FCanterbury, Faversham, Maidstone,
OL,17,FSevenoaks, Snodland, Tenterden and
OL,18,FTunbridge Wells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
